restro-works-app/
│── backend/ (Node + Express + MongoDB)
│   ├── models/ (User, Menu, Order schemas)
│   ├── routes/ (auth, menu, order APIs)
│   └── server.js
│
│── frontend/ (React)
│   ├── src/components/ (Navbar, Menu, Cart, AdminDashboard)
│   ├── src/pages/ (Home, Login, Register, Orders, Admin)
│   ├── src/context/ (AuthContext, CartContext)
│   └── src/App.js
│
│── README.md
